{"tid":614374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【走資陰霾】彭博顯示港滙賣出價曾穿7.85 金管局未入市","createTime":"2018-04-02T12:54:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T12:54:47.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c5197ebb654c9bed8b047ac5d580156e1c298fb6","tid":614374,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T12:54:47.000Z","msg":"【走資陰霾】彭博顯示港滙賣出價曾穿7.85 金管局未入市<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180402&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58026684\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180402%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58026684&d=N8lFs%2BBFd7K%2F5w9DddVCbAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=ebd6fc86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180402%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58026684&h=3ebecb5e\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180402&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58026684</a><br />\n<br />\n彭博數據顯示，今日凌晨2時至5時期間，港滙賣出價（Ask price）曾跌穿每美元兌7.85弱方兌換保證水平。不過由於正值復活節假期，交易額料非常薄弱，該段時間港滙價格走勢波動，惟未見有7.85水平成交個案，原因是大部份買入價（Bid price）平均在7.848至7.849附近水平。<br />\n<br />\n至於路透社報價系統，則未見貼近或跌穿每美元兌7.85港元成交出現，最弱僅見7.8491。<br />\n<br />\n兩間報價機構均未顯示金管局有入市掃入港元行動。"}]}